The electoral commission has rescheduled the Machakos senatorial by-election from March 23, 2021 to March 18, 2021 so as to allow for a smooth running of the national examinations scheduled for the week of March 23.
Independent Electoral and Boundaries Commission (IEBC) Chairman Wafula Chebukati said they had been informed by the Ministry of Education that the national examinations have been scheduled for the week of March 23, thus conflicting with their initial schedule.



